SIGN 32 40
Musical Chairs Rules:
The goal of this event is to not 
be left without a chair.  Once 
the event begins you will circle 
around the table.  You must 
stay moving around it at all 
times until the GC/host blocks 
one then you must rush to a 
chair and sit down.  The one 
without a chair is out.  As the 
event goes on more and more 
chairs will be blocked.  Winner 
is last one with a chair.
SIGNEND
